OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FWet
OL,6,Fand cloudy for most of Saturday. A lot
OL,7,Fdrier on Sunday with cloudy periods
OL,8,Fthroughout. Further cloud and rain to
OL,9,Fbe expected on Monday. Temperatures
OL,10,Fslightly below average.
